Name: Suspicious Stuffed N' Mashed Potatoes
Desc: An exquisitely colorful dish. The colors are distinct, and the shape regular, promoting an anticipation that is choked in the crib by the bone-dry potato. Are you sure this is potato mash and not steamed egg yolks?
Effect: Restores 26% of Max HP to the selected character and regenerates 450 HP every 5s for 30s.
